---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="历史科普系列 - 林寸" description="用说书人的口吻讲述历史，成语溯源，知识包裹。">
  <section class="relative py-32 px-6">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <a href="/" class="text-gray-500 hover:text-white text-sm transition-colors mb-8 inline-block">← 返回首页</a>
      <div class="mb-12">
        <span class="text-amber-500 text-sm font-medium">视频创作</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mt-3">历史科普系列</h1>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 text-lg">用说书人的口吻讲述历史，成语溯源，知识包裹</p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-8 text-gray-400 leading-relaxed">
        <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/5">
          <h2 class="text-white text-xl font-bold mb-4">项目简介</h2>
          <p>历史不应该是枯燥的年代表。这个系列用林汉达《中国历史故事集》的风格，以说书人的口吻重新讲述历史故事——有悬念、有转折、有成语的来龙去脉。</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/5">
          <h2 class="text-white text-xl font-bold mb-4">创作风格</h2>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-amber-500 mt-1">•</span><span><strong class="text-white">说书人叙事</strong> — 口语化表达，有代入感</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-amber-500 mt-1">•</span><span><strong class="text-white">成语溯源</strong> — 每个成语背后都有故事</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-amber-500 mt-1">•</span><span><strong class="text-white">知识包裹</strong> — 在故事里藏知识，不知不觉就学了</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-amber-500 mt-1">•</span><span><strong class="text-white">六步模板</strong> — 时间锚→人物登场→矛盾→因果→高潮→点睛</span></li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white/5 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-white/5">
          <h2 class="text-white text-xl font-bold mb-4">进度</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div>
              <div class="flex justify-between text-sm mb-1"><span class="text-white">第1集脚本</span><span class="text-green-400">✅ 完成</span></div>
              <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm">4651字，已定稿</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <div class="flex justify-between text-sm mb-1"><span class="text-white">第1集配音/剪辑</span><span class="text-gray-500">⏳ 待开始</span></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
